@Barry Ancona

Barry, please just admit you're wrong. The only remotely plausible reading of "About" here is as "Approximately". No wordplay is present.

The clue was fine, in the sense that the answer was obvious from it. But the actual area of a regulation infield in more than twice the 8100 sq. ft. in the clue. Replacing "infield" with "diamond" was the obvious fix.

